maven is an automation project management tool developed by apache software
its based on POM [Project Object Model] 
its build too and manages dependencies .
its can build any number of projects in to desired output such as an JAR,WAR .
it's mostly used for java projects and its written in java too.

EAR - Enterprice Application Architecher
WAR - web Application Architecture 
JAR - Java Application Archecture 

 -----> if we have java code we convert into JAR  
        if we have HTML,CSS we  conert into WAR file 
